<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>GER 212.  Rural, Urban, Global: Germanic Geographies.  3 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Exploration of cities and places within the German-speaking world along with their correlative cultures. High-intermediate to advanced language training using authentic written, visual and oral texts. Course Information: May be repeated to a maximum of 6 hours. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=GER%20104" title="GER 104" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'GER 104');">GER 104</a> or the equivalent.<br/>
