ode" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'AH 233');">AH 233</a> or <a href="/search/?P=MOVI%20233" title="MOVI 233" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MOVI 233');">MOVI 233</a>.<br/>
